
Build image
docker build -t apache-ecs .

Test php
docker run -d -p 8080:80/tcp --name apache-ecs-1 --mount type=bind,source=/home/<user>/apache-standalone/info.php,target=/var/www/html/info.php apache-ecs

Run container
docker run -d -p 8080:80/tcp --name apache-ecs-1 apache-ecs

Run container with nfs mount
?? docker run -d -p 8080:80/tcp --name apache-ecs-1 apache-ecs --volume-driver=nfs -v <server>/<dir>:/usr/share/wordpress/wp-content/images
